OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FShowers,
OL,6,Flocally heavy, clearing to the east
OL,7,Fthis evening, leaving many areas dry
OL,8,Fwith clear spells. Some rain or
OL,9,Fshowers will continue across northern
OL,10,FScotland, with rain returning later to
OL,11,Fthe southwest. A chilly night,
OL,12,Fespecially in some rural spots.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FRather cloudy for most with
OL,15,Foutbreaks of rain or showers, possibly
OL,16,Fheavy and thundery, especially over
OL,17,FNorthern Ireland. Driest in eastern
OL,18,FEngland with warm spells of sunshine
OL,19,Fhere until later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
